bwapi

Enum TechType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TechType>
      • bwapi.TechType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<TechType>

    public enum TechType
extends Enum<TechType>
    The TechType (or Technology Type, also referred to as an Ability) represents a Unit's ability which can be researched with Unit.research(bwapi.TechType) or used with Unit.useTech(bwapi.TechType).

    In order for a Unit to use its own specialized ability, it must first be available and researched.

      • getWeapon

        public WeaponType getWeapon()
        Retrieves the Weapon that is attached to this tech type. A technology's WeaponType is used to indicate the range and behaviour of the ability when used by a Unit.
        Returns:
        WeaponType containing information about the ability's behavior. Returns WeaponType.None If there is no corresponding WeaponType.

      • requiredUnit

        public UnitType requiredUnit()
        Retrieves the UnitType required to research this technology. The required unit type must be a completed unit owned by the player researching the technology.
        Returns:
        UnitType that is needed to research this tech type. Returns UnitType.None if no unit is required to research this tech type.
